            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:509px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/B7/wKgBZ1iUIliAbG-TABHb70PaUSA26.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/B7/wKgBZ1iUIliAbG-TABHb70PaUSA26.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="184064781" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3517.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3517" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>孔庙和国子监
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="191414200">
            这里是国子监的琉璃牌坊，是三间四柱七楼庑殿顶式琉璃牌坊，建于乾隆四十八年。中间这个门，地上数条汉<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10638.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="白玉" target="_blank">白玉</a>石铺路，解说的大叔哄着我们一个个跨了过去，说我们是越了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/64473.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="龙门" target="_blank">龙门</a>。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_184064782" data-seq="184064879" data-pid="184064782" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3517">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6785246/184064782.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:849px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/B9/wKgBZ1iUIluANCgwAA4-ggNOnU899.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://a1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/B9/wKgBZ1iUIluANCgwAA4-ggNOnU899.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="184064782" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3517.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3517" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>孔庙和国子监
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_184064778" data-seq="184064875" data-pid="184064778" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3517">
