            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:509px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/B2/wKgBZ1iUIlKAPVAsAAyC-A3LqVI01.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/B2/wKgBZ1iUIlKAPVAsAAyC-A3LqVI01.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="184064778" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3517.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3517" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>孔庙和国子监
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="191417398">
            辟雍，是国子监的中心建筑。<br />
初到北方，看见结冰的河流便欢喜得不得了，水底下还有游动的鱼儿。这对幼儿园以后再没见过结冰河面的我来说，实在是太神奇啦。<br />
但是温度吧，真的就还好~南方孩子表示适应无压力，还是南方更冷些！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_184064779" data-seq="184064876" data-pid="184064779" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3517">
