        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3783.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3783" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="food"></i>簋街
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="191420450">
            出门在外，中饭都是随便应付，不如晚餐吃得走心。<br />
第一天晚上，想带大家想吃点好的，于是便来到了2012年来过的花家怡园。当年就是在簋街瞎找，被这极具<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>特色的四合院式门头和建筑给吸引了，误打误撞竟然还是家名牌，走廊上挂着各种名人光顾的照片。<br />
<br />
前方高能预警，体积庞大的小胖来袭。大家看店面就好，看店面就好！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_184064760" data-seq="184064857" data-pid="184064760" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3783">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6785246/184064760.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:849px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/85/wKgBZ1iUIiiAbafGAAr32pogtvc98.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://a2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/85/wKgBZ1iUIiiAbafGAAr32pogtvc98.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="184064760" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3783.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3783" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="food"></i>簋街
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="191421557">
            兜兜转转找了好久，手机低温还时不时没电，10分钟的路愣是带着大家走了40分钟，个个都走成了苦瓜脸。好在最后一刻找到，这里的菜色也没让大家失望。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_184064772" data-seq="184064869" data-pid="184064772" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3783">
