            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:509px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/A1/wKgBZ1iUIkOAT9Y2AA9mQjqz3YU44.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/A1/wKgBZ1iUIkOAT9Y2AA9mQjqz3YU44.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="184064772" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3783.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3783" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="food"></i>簋街
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_184064766" data-seq="184064863" data-pid="184064766" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3783">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6785246/184064766.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:509px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/93/wKgBZ1iUIjaABguiAAxaeO0u2wg08.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/93/wKgBZ1iUIjaABguiAAxaeO0u2wg08.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="184064766" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3783.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3783" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="food"></i>簋街
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="191430246">
            烤鸭是必点的，听说全聚德的烤鸭又贵又不好吃，性价比低，都是给游客吃个牌子。那就来一个花家的烤鸭吧！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_184064770" data-seq="184064867" data-pid="184064770" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3783">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6785246/184064770.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:509px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://a3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/9C/wKgBZ1iUIj6AQg6DAAsAZ38yd1g45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://a3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/9C/wKgBZ1iUIj6AQg6DAAsAZ38yd1g45.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="184064770" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3783.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3783" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="food"></i>簋街
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="191430519">
            身后就是专门的料理台，有技艺娴熟的大厨为我们片烤鸭。一旁的啤酒上桌时我的口型就是=口=这样的。<br />
烤鸭的吃法也的确讲究，面皮有三种口味，酱料也有三种口味；鸭肉一半是皮肉连体，一半是分体，以满足食客的不同喜好。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_184064769" data-seq="184064866" data-pid="184064769" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3783">
