                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3783.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3783" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="food"></i>簋街
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="191431051">
            冬天还有小龙虾，果断点了一份，虽是冰冻货，但烹饪得尚可。<br />
全桌最好吃的莫过于饮料边的那晚“蒜肠”了，蒜香扑鼻，肉味鲜美，口感爽脆，必须要隆重推荐！（此处有聚光灯）没吃完打包回家，又当了我一连两日的下饭菜，现在想起来，还馋得不行。回头我必须得淘宝一下&nbsp;看看有没有这等优质零食。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_184064773" data-seq="184064870" data-pid="184064773" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3783">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6785246/184064773.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:849px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/A4/wKgBZ1iUIkaAQKTQAAvzqsAtLK063.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/A4/wKgBZ1iUIkaAQKTQAAvzqsAtLK063.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="184064773" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3783.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3783" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="food"></i>簋街
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="191431970">
            这酒，壮观吧
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_184064767" data-seq="184064864" data-pid="184064767" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3783">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_6785246/184064767.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:509px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/94/wKgBZ1iUIjiAel6nAA3KcwR_BzI11.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/95/94/wKgBZ1iUIjiAel6nAA3KcwR_BzI11.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90" data-pid="184064767" alt="" />
        </a>
